data.description: Welcome to Rustic Florida living at its finest! NO HOA...NO CDD...NO FLOOD ZONE and a POOL on 1 ACRE of land. This 3/2/2 2303 sq foot home is an exquisite piece of property that is ready for a new family to call it home. The home comes equip with beautiful luxury vinyl flooring, tile and carpeted bedrooms to keep those feet warm. There is an amazing BONUS room perfect for a game room, entertaining, or even an office. A large lanai is a door away and leads you out back to the pool and serene nature of Florida living. A U-Pick orange grove is located next door which is open six months out of the year and is great if you want to squeeze your own OJ. No rear or front neighbors!! Minutes away from shopping, water access, and major highways. Don't let this home pass you by.
